@startuml seq_13_post_comment
title Sequence Diagram: UC-13 Post Comment

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Comment Controller" as Controller
participant "Comment Service" as Service
participant "Post Repo" as PostRepo
participant "Comment Repo" as CommentRepo
participant "Event Bus\n(Go Channels)" as EventBus

User -> Frontend: Write & submit comment
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/posts/{post_id}/comments {content}
Controller -> Service: Create Comment
Service -> PostRepo: Verify post exists and allows comments
PostRepo --> Service: Post is valid

Service -> CommentRepo: Insert new Comment record
CommentRepo --> Service: Comment created
Service -> PostRepo: Increment post comment count
PostRepo --> Service: Count updated

Service -> EventBus: Publish CommentCreatedEvent
note right of EventBus
  Background goroutine notifies
  the post author
end note

Service --> Controller: Created Comment Data
Controller --> Frontend: 201 Created
Frontend --> User: Render new comment in thread
@enduml